    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil kettle</p><p>Heat a dry pot (with a matching lid) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> pine nuts</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and lightly golden</p><p>Set them aside and reserve the pot</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-sun-dried-tomato-pesto-orzo-with-mozzarella/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and dice</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-sun-dried-tomato-pesto-orzo-with-mozzarella/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>orzo </strong>to the reserved pot with your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>diced pepper </strong>and cover with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>orzo</strong> for 6-8 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-sun-dried-tomato-pesto-orzo-with-mozzarella/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-sun-dried-tomato-pesto-orzo-with-mozzarella/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> basil </strong>finely, including the stalks</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-sun-dried-tomato-pesto-orzo-with-mozzarella/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once your orzo is cooked, drain and then return it to the pot, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-sun-dried-tomato-pesto-orzo-with-mozzarella/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>sun-dried tomato pesto</strong>, <strong>soft cheese </strong>and the <strong>torn mozzarella </strong>to the pot with a splash of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>one pot sun-dried tomato pesto orzo with mozzarella</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/one-pot-sun-dried-tomato-pesto-orzo-with-mozzarella/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one pot sun-dried tomato pesto orzo with mozzarella</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted pine nuts</strong>,<strong> chopped basil </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
